<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 09:13:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>克里姆林宫表示，俄罗斯考虑降低与西方的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-considering-downgrading-relations-with-west-kremlin-says-2024-06-27/</link><description>克里姆林宫周四表示，由于美国及其盟国进一步卷入乌克兰战争，俄罗斯正在考虑可能降级与西方的外交关系，但尚未做出任何决定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 09:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-considering-downgrading-relations-with-west-kremlin-says-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>随着印度活动激增，亚洲将成为股权交易热点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asia-emerge-equity-deals-hot-spot-india-activity-surges-2024-06-27/</link><description>银行家和分析师表示，中国监管机构批准数量增加后，香港首次公开募股可能会复苏，而印度的一​​系列大型交易预计将使亚洲成为今年下半年股权交易的亮点。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 08:20:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asia-emerge-equity-deals-hot-spot-india-activity-surges-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国芯片制造商 Nexperia 投资 2 亿美元拓展欧洲业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-owned-chipmaker-nexperia-invests-200-mln-european-expansion-2024-06-27/</link><description>全球最大的二极管和晶体管等基础半导体制造商之一安世半导体周四表示，将投资 2 亿美元扩大其位于德国汉堡的主要生产基地的产能。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 08:11:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-owned-chipmaker-nexperia-invests-200-mln-european-expansion-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>台湾警告不要在处决威胁后前往中国大陆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-tells-its-citizens-avoid-unnecessary-travel-china-2024-06-27/</link><description>继北京上周威胁处决那些被视为“顽固”台独支持者之后，台湾政府周四提高了对中国大陆的旅行警告，告诉其公民除非绝对必要，否则不要前往。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 08:09:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-tells-its-citizens-avoid-unnecessary-travel-china-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>日本队将在世界杯预选赛第三阶段对阵沙特阿拉伯、澳大利亚</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/japanese-face-saudi-arabia-australia-third-phase-world-cup-qualifiers-2024-06-27/</link><description>四届亚洲冠军日本队周四将在 2026 年世界杯预选赛亚洲区第三轮比赛中面对熟悉的对手，守安肇的球队周四在吉隆坡对阵澳大利亚、沙特阿拉伯、巴林、中国和印度尼西亚。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 08:05:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/japanese-face-saudi-arabia-australia-third-phase-world-cup-qualifiers-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国希望与欧盟达成适合双方的电动汽车关税协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-hopes-reach-mutually-acceptable-solutions-with-eu-ev-tariffs-2024-06-27/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国希望与欧盟就定于 7 月 4 日生效的中国电动汽车初步关税谈判达成“双方都能接受的解决方案”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 07:32:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-hopes-reach-mutually-acceptable-solutions-with-eu-ev-tariffs-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>尽管央行警告风险，中国资金仍流入债券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-money-flows-into-bonds-even-central-bank-warns-risks-2024-06-27/</link><description>中国国债期货周四跃升至新高，而长期收益率则触及历史低点，因为投资者无视央行一再发出的风险警告，继续将资金投入债券。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 07:22:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-money-flows-into-bonds-even-central-bank-warns-risks-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国主导俄罗斯电动汽车市场，Zeekr 销量猛增</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/zeekrs-sales-jump-chinese-dominate-russian-ev-market-2024-06-27/</link><description>去年，Zeekr 电动汽车在俄罗斯的销量猛增，使中国汽车制造商在俄罗斯规模虽小但发展迅速的电动汽车 (EV) 行业中处于领先地位。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 07:03:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/zeekrs-sales-jump-chinese-dominate-russian-ev-market-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，中国共产党将于 7 月 15 日至 18 日举行重要的三中全会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-hold-key-third-plenum-july-15-18-state-media-say-2024-06-27/</link><description>据新华社周四报道，中国共产党将于 7 月 15 日至 18 日举行拖延已久的三中全会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 05:45:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-hold-key-third-plenum-july-15-18-state-media-say-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>回收将成为应对欧盟稀土挑战的长期解决方案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/recycling-kick-long-term-solution-eu-rare-earths-challenge-2024-06-27/</link><description>欧盟公司正准备利用巨大的回收潜力，为欧盟的绿色转型提供关键的稀土，但需要一段时间才能有足够的旧电动汽车和风力涡轮机供应来进行处理。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:12:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/recycling-kick-long-term-solution-eu-rare-earths-challenge-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>将稀土从矿山转化为磁体的复杂性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/complexity-transforming-rare-earths-mine-magnet-2024-06-27/</link><description>欧盟将努力实现旨在提高国内关键矿物产量并减少对中国依赖的新立法中有关稀土的雄心勃勃的目标。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:06:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/complexity-transforming-rare-earths-mine-magnet-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>在夺回稀土荣耀的竞赛中，欧洲未能实现矿产目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/race-regain-rare-earth-glory-europe-falls-short-mineral-goals-2024-06-27/</link><description>四十年前，法国大西洋沿岸的一家稀土加工厂是世界上最大的稀土加工厂之一，生产用于制造彩色电视、弧光灯和相机镜头的材料。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:04:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/race-regain-rare-earth-glory-europe-falls-short-mineral-goals-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，腾讯支持的 Shift Up IPO 定价可能处于上限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tencent-backed-shift-up-may-price-ipo-top-end-band-source-says-2024-06-27/</link><description>据知情人士透露，由中国腾讯支持的韩国游戏公司 Shift Up 计划将其首次公开募股定价在其定价范围的高端，并筹集 4,350 亿韩元（3.13 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 03:45:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tencent-backed-shift-up-may-price-ipo-top-end-band-source-says-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>通胀数据公布前欧洲股市持稳，日元接近 38 年低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-27/</link><description>周四早盘交易中，欧洲股市苦苦寻找方向，交易员等待关键通胀数据，而市场也对日本当局在日元进一步下跌后干预日元的迹象保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 02:21:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>母公司香港交易所表示，伦敦金属交易所(LME)将香港视为全球仓库所在地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lme-eyes-hong-kong-potential-warehouse-location-hkex-ceo-says-2024-06-27/</link><description>伦敦金属交易所（LME）首席执行官周四表示，该交易所正在探索将香港列为 LME 仓库地点的可能性，因为该交易所希望加强其全球物流足迹。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 01:43:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lme-eyes-hong-kong-potential-warehouse-location-hkex-ceo-says-2024-06-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>